OL,3,CTwo more men charged with murder after
OL,4,CPrimrose Hill stabbing
OL,6,FTwo further men have been charged with
OL,7,Fmurder in connection with a fatal
OL,8,Fstabbing on Primrose Hill, police have
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FAlexis Bidace, 25, of Fore Street,
OL,12,FEnfield, north London, and Ernest
OL,13,FBoateng, 25, of Keswick Drive,
OL,14,FEnfield, were arrested on Monday and
OL,15,Fhave since been charged with murder.
OL,17,FThey will both appear at Wimbledon
OL,18,FMagistrates' Court on Wednesday, the
OL,19,FMetropolitan Police said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
