OL,3,CTwo more men charged with murder after
OL,4,CPrimrose Hill stabbing
OL,6,FFinbar Sullivan, 21, a filmmaking
OL,7,Fstudent, was stabbed to death in the
OL,8,Fearly evening on Tuesday April 7 at
OL,9,Fthe viewpoint in north London.
OL,11,FTwo other men have previously been
OL,12,Farrested in connection with his death.
OL,14,FOliuwadamilola Ogunyankinnu, 27, of
OL,15,FSouthbury Road, Enfield, was charged
OL,16,Fwith the student's murder on Sunday
OL,17,Fand he appeared at Stratford
OL,18,FMagistrates' Court on Monday. He was
OL,19,Fremanded in custody.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
