OL,3,CTwo more men charged with murder after
OL,4,CPrimrose Hill stabbing
OL,6,FKhalid Abdulqadir, 18, of Fellows
OL,7,FRoad, Camden, was charged with
OL,8,Fgrievous bodily harm, violent disorder
OL,9,Fand possession of a knife. He appeared
OL,10,Fat Wimbledon Magistrates' Court on
OL,11,FTuesday and was remanded in custody.
OL,13,FAnyone with information should contact
OL,14,Fpolice, quoting reference 6448/07Apr,
OL,15,Fas the investigation continues.
